o multi-criteria calibration strategies using the\nselected signatures, including a single-objective optimization approach, which\ntransforms the multi-criteria problem into a single-objective function, and a\nmulti-objective optimization approach, which uses a simple additive weighting\nmethod to select an optimal solution from the Pareto set. Our results show\nsignificant improvements in both calibration and temporal validation metrics,\nespecially for flood signatures, demonstrating the robustness and delicacy of\nour signatures-based calibration framework for enhancing flash flood\nforecasting systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 May 2023 17:23:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-01"}
