lose to the star. We show that the same conclusions\nare valid for the constraints on atmospheric parameters such as the C/O ratio,\nmetallicity, surface gravity, and temperature, while higher spectral resolution\n(R~10,000) is required to constrain the radial velocity and spin of the planet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 May 2023 18:40:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-01"}
