\nSMC has an SMC origin, and the other two southern regions have a mix of LMC and\nSMC origins. Our results add to the evidence that the southern substructures of\nthe LMC periphery are the product of close interactions between the LMC and\nSMC, and thus likely hold important clues that can constrain models of their\ndetailed dynamical histories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 May 2023 00:01:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-01"}
